name: Gravity Study 02 - Wells
description:
In this interactive generative piece, users are the artists, placing colorful streamers that orbit gravity wells.

Instructions:
Click or tap to place a streamer.

SPACE BAR to toggle the background between black and white.

SHIFT key to toggle visibility of the gravity wells.

RIGHT ARROW to toggle "streamers live forever" mode, which enables them to continue orbiting until you press the Right Arrow key again.

LEFT ARROW key to reset the piece and start again.
